snippet.textDisplay:
Tip for anyone who is sick right now:
Instead of drinking some magic OJ, use the b.r.a.t diet. B.r.a.t, in this case, stands for:
Bananas
Rice
Applesauce
Toast
Why these things in particular? It’s because if you have an upset stomach you don’t want it to work any harder than it has to. All of these things, (as well as eggs, crackers and bread) are easy to digest.
Things like steak, milk, fried and greasy foods are difficult to break down, so if you’re hurling your guts out you may want to avoid those.
Hope this helped someone out there who’s dying to death right now.
